TXL Example Specification
-------------------------

Name:   
        ISL.Txl

Description:
        Prototype implementation of transformation of Project REX
        Interface Specification Language (ISL) to programming-language
        dependent interface files.  
        
        This specification handles stage 1, the language-independent 
        ISL->ISL part of the transforms, which converts to declaration-
        before-use from free-form, resolves generic and parameterized 
        types, and converts the type dependencies from structural-
        equivalence (ISL) to name-equivalence (most target languages).

Author:
        J.R. Cordy

Affiliation:
        Esprit Project REX
        Gesellschaft fuer Mathematik und Datenverarbeitung,
        Forschungstelle an der Universitaet Karlsruhe,
        Karlsruhe, Germany

Date:
        November 1990

Example:
        txl Example.ISL 
